item.title: CVE-2023-2964|2024-08-02T06:41:04.088Z -- unknown -- simple%20iframe
item.description: The Simple Iframe WordPress plugin before 1.2.0 does not properly validate one of its WordPress block attribute's content, which may allow users whose role is at least that of a contributor to conduct Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
